dict.string: This is just a sample. Do NOT try loading it.
Ensure you understand EVERY field before booting.
In most cases recommended to use Sample.plist
Use SampleLegacy.plist for end of life models: 2011 and older.
Haswell: SB_RCBA is a 0x4 page memory region, containing SPI_BASE at 0x3800 (SPI_BASE_ADDRESS)
Generic: PCI root is a 0x1000 page memory region used by some firmwares
change F%uT%04x to F%uTxxxx in AppleBacklightInjector.kext (credit RehabMan)
Prevent Apple I2C kexts from attaching to I2C controllers, credit CoolStar
Prevent Apple I2C kexts from attaching to I2C controllers, credit CoolStar
Disable Intel, Fresco Logic USB3.0 controllers check, 10.9.* (credit Zenith432)
Disable Intel, Fresco Logic USB3.0 controllers check, 10.10.* (credit Zenith432)
Patch MSI or pin interrupts #1, 10.9.*, 10.10.* (credit Zenith432)
Patch MSI or pin interrupts #2, 10.10.* (credit Zenith432)
Disable the sleep code leaving the controller in non-working state after wake, 10.9.*, 10.10.* (credit Zenith432)
Enable PCI power management if there is no such code in DSDT, 10.9.*, 10.10.* (credit Zenith432)
